videos.headline: Staley extols the importance of Gamecocks' post players
videos.description: After an SEC tourney semifinal win over Ole Miss, Dawn Staley explains how crucial South Carolina's post players are when it comes to experience and communication.

videos.headline: 1-seed South Carolina holds off gritty 4-seed Rebels
videos.description: Aliyah Boston helps the Gamecocks fend off Ole Miss' comeback attempt to win 61-51 and advance to the SEC Championship game.
